Dialogue: 0,00:21:49.92,00:21:52.11,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不断追赶着你
Dialogue: 0,00:21:52.11,00:21:54.28,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}直至引以自豪
Dialogue: 0,00:21:54.31,00:21:58.35,ed1cn,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们都不会放弃
